    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm having a bit of a tough time with my team. I have two direct reports who are constantly undermining each other during our weekly syncs. It's getting really unprofessional—they'll interrupt each other or make snide comments about the other person's work in front of everyone. It's starting to affect the rest of the team's morale too. How should I handle this?",
